Ford Exploring Options for Volvo Auto Bank as Sale Talks Fail

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-09-23T21:03:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/ford-exploring-options-for-volvo-auto-bank-as-sale-talks-fail.html
Ford Motor Co. (F)  is exploring options
for Volvo Auto Bank Deutschland GmbH after negotiations with
potential buyers failed, a spokeswoman said.  “It will be business as usual” for the bank’s 100
employees in  Germany  until a solution is found, Ford spokeswoman
Margaret Mellot said in a telephone interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in Frankfurt at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
